document: {"blocks":[{"key":"84rhb","text":"Liberty CBD Gummy Bears are known for their high antioxidant content. They contain a very rich concentration of the potent antioxidant, lycopene which is the red pigment in tomatoes. Lycopene has the ability to neutralize free radicals that can damage cells in the body. Lycopene excels as the most effective antioxidant promoter of heart health. Lycopene may have specific properties that enable it to protect cells in a way other antioxidants may not. Sufficient levels of lycopene have been shown to lessen the chances of those suffering an ischemic stroke. This type of stroke is caused by a blood clot and it is the most common type of stroke. Tomatoes also contain phytonutrients which support heart health.
